duties_responsibilities.duty: Perform routine semi-technical program work related to the Unemployment Insurance (UI) program.
Provide telephone advisory duties related to registration for the Benefit Program Online and navigation through UI Online and State Information Data Exchange System.
Handle less complex technical work related to UI benefit claim and payment activities.
Conduct position at EDD office located in Rancho Cordova and remotely.
Fluency in the Spanish language is required.

education_certification.credential: Fluency in the Spanish language is required.
